{"tid":2087114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我只係睇到黃之鋒、周庭、羅冠聰捨身取義","createTime":"2020-06-30T14:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T14:57:32.000Z","uid":93980,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb8e96778480969626d7c8bf00aaa611d55861d","tid":2087114,"uid":93980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:53:47.000Z","msg":"好多人話黃之鋒、周庭、羅冠聰退出眾志係笠水，但我睇到係捨身取義既精神。佢地一方面面對住中共，一方面背後有好多黨員，佢地比中共搞就梗，但佢地無直接話金盆洗手，而係為左保護黨友而自己將所有責任拎上身。<br />\n<br />\n以前我會覺得香港人口裡說犧牲，但真係肯犧牲又有幾多？今日見到除左黃之鋒、周庭、羅冠聰之外，仲有張菎陽等人為左保護黨友而以自己一己之力繼續抗爭，作為香港人，見到班咁既年青人，我覺得好驕傲。<br />\n<br />\n７１維園見"},{"pid":"acaac46a4c5ad6021df12ecda9f16044e38e8700","tid":2087114,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:54:25.000Z","msg":"陳雲都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10d571213e5fc71f180b967d4dd8d722784e557","tid":2087114,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTcqtv8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTcqtv8.jpg&h=e8794907&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nFUsGQ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnFUsGQ8.png&h=fe7230d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58a698c6a3c93ac637346552c10904b1095633ba","tid":2087114,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acaac46a4c5ad6021df12ecda9f16044e38e8700","tid":2087114,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:54:25.000Z","msg":"陳雲都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa